parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle loses power
the engine dies
the dash indicates a battery problem
the vehicle is unable to restart
the electrical components flash off and on
the media center is blank
the backup camera fails
the vehicle's systems associated with the media center do not work.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the idle stop/start system can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls after the idle stop/start system is enacted
the engine cuts out completely
the vehicle requires a restart
the vehicle lurches forward before stalling.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning of the sliding doors can cause injuries or accidents, especially when the doors close on their own or fail to open properly.
symptoms: The sliding doors close on their own
the doors do not fully open
the doors close abruptly
the doors fail to open when the lock button is pressed
the doors cause injuries or accidents.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the infotainment system can cause distractions while driving, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: The media center is blank
the backup camera fails
the systems associated with the media center do not work
crackling noises come from the speakers
the infotainment screen continuously reboots.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning of the collision mitigation braking system can cause accidents or near-misses, especially when the system applies the brakes unnecessarily.
symptoms: The collision mitigation braking system is applied unnecessarily
the vehicle stops abruptly
the message "brake" is displayed on the instrument panel.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose acceleration, leading to a loss of control, which can result in accidents, injuries, or even death.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly loses acceleration
the engine revs without forward motion
the transmission shifts into neutral without warning
the vehicle slows down without warning
the RPM needles oscillate quickly between gears
the infotainment system freezes
and the transmission temperature warning light appears.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended activation of the Automatic Emergency Braking (AEB) system can cause sudden and unexpected stops, increasing the risk of rear-end collisions and accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly brakes for no reason
the "BREAK" sign appears on the instrument dashboard
a beep is emitted
the vehicle comes to a halt without warning
the vehicle auto-brakes without any obstacles or cars in front of it.
